        <h3>Description</h3>
        <ol>
            <li>Pick The items you want</li>
            <li>Choose how many of each item you want</li>
            <li>Choose the quality of the item</li>
            <li>Copy to your clipboard</li>
            <li> Press " ` " when you are in the game to open the console</li>
